quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,94,Whenever We sent a Prophet to a town We afflicted its people with adversity and misfortunes so that they might humble themselves
  7,95,"Then We changed their adversity into good fortune till they became very affluent and said: \"Our forefathers also had their adversity and affluence.\" Behold! We took them by surprise while they did not even notice it"
  7,96,"Had the residents of the towns believed and feared Allah, We would have showered upon them riches from the heavens and the earth, but they disbelieved; so We seized them for their misdeeds"
  7,97,Do the people of these towns now feel secure from Our punishment coming to them by night while they might be fast asleep
  7,98,Or do the people of these towns feel secure from Our punishment coming to them in broad daylight while they are playing around
  7,99,"Do these people feel secure against the plan of Allah? In fact, only those people feel secure from the plan of Allah who are doomed to destruction"